CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 18, reads: "...6. Representative for the Natural Gas Companies, James P. Griffin and Miss Noraella Brown, gas appliance demonstrator, in their impressive-looking booth..."
TitMainTitle: James P. Griffin and Noraella Brown standing Natural Gas Companies booth in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
